## How to Publish on GitHub  
1. Create a repository named `photoshop-clone-stamp-docs`.  
2. Save this text as `README.md` in the main folder.  
3. Add images to an `images/` subfolder and update the links above.  
4. Use [GitHub Pages](https://pages.github.com/) to host the documentation as a website.  

